title: Fleetwood Mac - The Rosebud Film (1977) DVD5
description:
Fleetwood Mac: 'The Rosebud Film' by Michael Collins is a 1977
documentary created to promote the European leg of the 'Rumours'
tour. It includes some behind-the-scenes interviews, rehearsal
footage and live performances.
